0the%20top%20three%20batters%20can%20break%20the%20record%20of%2050%20ODI%20centuries%20and%20the%20middle-order%20can't%20break%20it.%20We%20have%20Babar%20Azam%20who%20can%20break%20it.%20They%20have%20Shubman%20Gill%20who%20can%20chase%20the%20record)%2C%26quot%3B%20Akmal%20said%20on%20ARY%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%20surpassed%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20to%20become%20the%20first%20player%20in%20the%20history%20of%20ODI%20cricket%20to%20score%2050%20centuries.%20Moments%20later%20Virat's%20gesture%20stole%20the%20show%20as%20he%20bowed%20to%20Sachin%20who%20was%20applauding%20in%20the%20stands%20witnessing%20the%20star%20batter%20breaking%20his%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat%20scored%20117%20in%20113%20balls%20in%20the%20first%20semi-final%20match%20against%20New%20Zealand.%20His%20knock%20consisted%20of%20nine%20fours%20and%20two%20sixes.%20Virat%20scored%20his%20runs%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20over%20103.%20He%20was%20eventually%20dismissed%20by%20Tim%20Southee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India's%2010%20matches%20of%20the%20tournament%2C%20the%2035-year-old%20has%20scored%20691%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%20115.16%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20over%2089.%20His%20best%20score%20is%20117.%20Virat%20has%20scored%20three%20centuries%20and%20five%20fifties%20in%2010%20innings%20in%20the%20tournament%20and%20is%20the%20highest%20run-getter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20India%20skipper%20has%20scored%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20runs%20in%20a%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20edition%2C%20going%20past%20Sachin's%20record%20of%20673%20runs%20in%20the%202003%20edition%20of%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700304300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fr1blsr18_virat-kohli-babar-azam-afp_625x300_06_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fwho-can-break-virat-kohlis-50-odi-tons-record-ex-pakistan-star-says-babar-azam-and-4581236%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%20surpassed%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20to%20become%20the%20first%20player%20in%20the%20history%20of%20ODI%20cricket%20to%20score%2050%20centuries.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fwho-can-break-virat-kohlis-50-odi-tons-record-ex-pakistan-star-says-babar-azam-and-4581236%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fwho-can-break-virat-kohlis-50-odi-tons-record-ex-pakistan-star-says-babar-azam-and-4581236%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fwho-can-break-virat-kohlis-50-odi-tons-record-ex-pakistan-star-says-babar-azam-and-4581236%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sentences%20Gain%20More%20Persuasion%20When%20Written%20In%20Present%20Tense%3A%20Study%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERecent%20research%20unveils%20that%2C%20although%20people%20commonly%20narrate%20events%20in%20the%20past%20tense%2C%20conveying%20the%20information%20in%20the%20present%20tense%20enhances%20the%20speaker's%20or%20writer's%20certainty%2C%20thereby%20increasing%20persuasiveness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20University%20of%20Toronto%20study%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fpii%2FS0022103123001014%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EJournal%20of%20Experimental%20Social%20Psychology%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Easserts%20that%20any%20message%20specially%20the%20online%20reviews%20articulated%20in%20the%20present%20tense%20holds%20greater%20persuasive%20power%20compared%20to%20other%20forms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResearchers%20says%20that's%20because%20the%20present%20tense%20makes%20a%20message%20seem%20more%20specific%20and%20concrete%2C%20which%20helps%20audiences%20better%20visualize%20its%20meaning%20and%20feel%20psychologically%20closer%20to%20the%20author.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20more%20vivid%20something%20is%2C%20the%20more%20real%20and%20true%20it%20seems%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Sam%20Maglio%2C%20co-author%20of%20the%20study%20and%20professor%20of%20marketing%20and%20psychology%20at%20U%20of%20T%20Scarborough.%20%26quot%3BThe%20past%20and%20the%20future%20aren't%20as%20vivid%20as%20the%20present.%20In%20the%20present%20tense%2C%20you%20as%20the%20reader%20take%20a%20journey%20with%20the%20speaker%20and%20you%20become%20immersed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20experiencing%20it%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaglio%2C%20along%20with%20David%20Fang%2C%20a%20U%20of%20T%20alumnus%2C%20examined%20millions%20of%20Amazon%20reviews%20to%20determine%20the%20impact%20of%20verb%20tense%20on%20helpfulness%20ratings.%20They%20found%20that%20reviews%20written%20in%20the%20present%20tense%20received%20significantly%20more%20upvotes%20than%20those%20written%20in%20the%20past%20or%20future%20tense.%20This%20trend%20persisted%20even%20when%20considering%20other%20factors%20such%20as%20pictures%2C%20review%20length%2C%20and%20star%20ratings.%20Additionally%2C%20when%20hundreds%20of%20participants%20were%20asked%20to%20rate%20reviews%2C%20they%20consistently%20favored%20those%20written%20in%20the%20present%20tense.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReviews%20are%20maximally%20helpful%20when%20they%20are%20right%20here%20and%20they're%20right%20now%20because%20the%20closer%20the%20reader%20can%20come%20to%20seeing%20it%2C%20touching%20it%2C%20making%20it%20palpable%2C%20the%20more%20they%20believe%20it%20and%20the%20more%20they%20trust%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Maglio%2C%20who%20is%20cross-appointed%20to%20the%20Rotman%20School%20of%20Management.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20hard%20to%20be%20immersive%20and%20vivid%20and%20visceral%20from%20a%20world%20away.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700304060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F4ilphvd8_laptop-generic-reuters-laptops-generic-reuters_625x300_05_August_23.jpg%22%