ivali%20area%20of%20Mumbai%20and%20when%20his%20uncle%20came%20to%20meet%20Lad%2C%20the%20coach%20insisted%20for%20Rohit%20to%20be%20admitted%20to%20Swami%20Vivekanand%20School.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHis%20uncle%20told%20me%20that%20the%20school%20where%20he%20was%20studying%20charged%20only%20Rs%2030%2C%20and%20that%20they%20couldn't%20afford%20to%20pay%20Rs%20275.%20Which%20is%20when%20I%20requested%20the%20director%20to%20give%20him%20a%20freeship%20(financial%20aid%20provided%20to%20students%20from%20economically%20weaker%20sections).%20He%20is%20the%20first%20student%20whom%20I%20requested%20a%20freeship%20for.%20The%20director%20did%20ask%20me%20why%20I%20was%20supporting%20this%20student.%20But%20I%20knew%20he%20was%20bright%20and%20played%20good%20cricket.%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20let%20him%20go%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Lad%20according%20to%20News18.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20proved%20to%20be%20the%20turning%20point%20in%20his%20career%20as%20he%20flourished%20under%20the%20coaching%20of%20Dinesh%20Lad%20and%20he%20went%20on%20to%20play%20U-19%20cricket%20and%20domestic%20cricket%20before%20finally%20breaking%20into%20the%20senior%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700303880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Ff5bi2ar8_rohit-sharma_625x300_18_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fodi-cricket-world-cup-2023-final-rohit-sharmas-family-couldnt-afford-to-pay-rs-275-school-fees-rest-is-history-4585065%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20Final%3A%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20journey%20to%20superstardom%20started%20with%20an%20interesting%20incident%20regarding%20his%20cricket%20coaching.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fodi-cricket-world-cup-2023-final-rohit-sharmas-family-couldnt-afford-to-pay-rs-275-school-fees-rest-is-history-4585065%22%2C%22cdnA