0video%20app%20of%20%26quot%3Bcreating%20the%20biggest%20antisemitic%20movement%20since%20the%20Nazis%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20The%20New%20York%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20accusation%20comes%20amid%20growing%20concerns%20about%20TikTok's%20role%20in%20fostering%20an%20alleged%20surge%20of%20antisemitic%20abuse%20on%20its%20platform%20and%20wider%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20%3Cspan%3EFacebook%20cofounder%20Dustin%20Moskovitz%2C%20now%20the%20CEO%20of%20Asana%2C%20said%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-ceo-elon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20should%20resign%20after%20Musk%20described%20an%20antisemitic%20post%20on%20X%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bactual%20truth.%26quot%3B%20Meanwhile%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fibm-pulls-advertising-x-report-finds-ads-antisemitic-posts-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIBM%20announced%20the%20suspension%20of%20advertising%20on%20X%20%3C%2Fa%3Efollowing%20allegations%20that%20its%20ads%20appeared%20alongside%20pro-Nazi%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20criticism%20against%20TikTok%20intensified%20as%20the%20platform%20faced%20allegations%20of%20inadequately%20addressing%20pro-Hamas%20propaganda%20and%20antisemitic%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBaron%20Cohen%20told%20TikTok%20executives%2C%20%26quot%3Bshame%20on%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20for%20allegedly%20promoting%20hate%20through%20the%20content%20circulated%20on%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20Baron%20Cohen%20has%20taken%20social%20media%20chiefs%20to%20task%20for%20failing%20to%20control%20hate%20speech%20on%20their%20lucrative%20and%20influential%20platforms.%20While%20presenting%20at%20the%20Golden%20Globes%20in%202020%2C%20he%20mocked%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsacha-baron-cohen-tore-into-mark-zuckerberg-again-at-the-golden-globes-2020-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFacebook%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3Enaive%2C%20misguided%20child%20who%20spreads%20Nazi%20propaganda.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20call%20was%20initiated%20by%20TikTok%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20address%20the%20escalating%20antisemitism%20controversy%20following%20an%20open%20letter%20signed%20by%20Jewish%20celebrities%20and%20influencers%20declaring%20the%20app%20%26quot%3Bnot%20safe%20for%20Jewish%20users.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreators%20and%20celebrities%20on%20the%20call%20described%20receiving%20comments%20like%20%26quot%3BHitler%20was%20right%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BI%20hope%20you%20end%20up%20like%20Anne%20Frank%26quot%3B%20under%20videos%20posted%20by%20them%20and%20other%20Jewish%20users%2C%20per%20The%20New%20York%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20call%2C%20Baron%20Cohen%20drew%20parallels%20between%20the%20influence%20of%20TikTok%20and%20the%20use%20of%20propaganda%20that%20led%20to%20violent%20acts.%20He%20cited%20the%20example%20of%20the%20October%207%20attacks%2C%20attributing%20the%20ability%20of%20groups%20like%20Hamas%20to%20commit%20heinous%20acts%20to%20the%20exposure%20of%20hateful%20images%20from%20a%20young%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20platform%20contends%20that%20the%20prevalence%20of%20pro-Palestinian%20posts%20reflects%20the%20views%20of%20millennials%20rather%20than%20any%20orchestrated%20bias.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20call%20also%20featured%20actors%20Amy%20Schumer%20and%20Will%20%26amp%3B%20Grace%20star%20Debra%20Messing%2C%20engaging%20in%20a%20dialogue%20with%20TikTok%20executives%20Adam%20Presser%20and%20Seth%20Melnick.%20Presser%20acknowledged%20the%20validity%20of%20Baron%20Cohen's%20concerns%2C%20admitting%20that%20social%20media%20companies%2C%20including%20TikTok%2C%20must%20combat%20hate%20content%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOsama%20bin%20Laden's%20'Letter%20to%20America'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223744%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amy%20Schumer%20performing%20onstage%20in%20a%20white%20dress.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6557aa714ca513d8242b8c05%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222496%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmy%20Schumer%20performs%20onstage%20at%20the%202023%20Good%2BFoundation%20%26quot%3BA%20Very%20Good%2B%20Night%20of%20Comedy%26quot%3B%20Benefit%20at%20Carnegie%20Hall%20on%20October%2018%2C%202023%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3Cp%3EJamie%20McCarthy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20reached%20a%20tipping%20point%20when%20users%20began%20posting%20a%20letter%20written%20by%20Osama%20bin%20Laden%2021%20years%20ago%20under%20the%20hashtag%20%23lettertoamerica.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%2C%20which%20rationalizes%20the%209%2F11%20attacks%20and%20advocates%20for%20revenge%20against%20%26quot%3BAmericans%20and%20Jews%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20deleted%20by%20The%20Guardian%20after%20being%20widely%20shared%20on%20social%20media%20without%20proper%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%20denied%20that%20the%20letter%20went%20viral%20on%20its%20platform%2C%20asserting%20that%20the%20%23lettertoamerica%20hashtag%20had%20a%20minimal%20impact%20compared%20to%20more%20popular%20topics.%20Despite%20removing%20the%20hashtag%2C%20the%20company%20maintains%20that%20the%20situation%20is%20not%20a%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnikki-haley-vivek-ramaswamy-tiktok-gop-debate-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERepublican%20presidential%20hopeful%20Nikki%20Haley%20has%20joined%20the%20chorus%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20advocating%20for%20a%20TikTok%20ban%2C%20per%20The%20New%20York%20Times.%20She%20expressed%20concern%20that%20thousands%20of%20TikTok%20users%20were%20supporting%20Osama%20Bin%20Laden's%20ideology%2C%20using%20it%20as%20an%20example%20of%20how%20foreign%20adversaries%20exploit%20social%20media%20to