%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FcTFYAeasqOk%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22REALITY%20of%20Driving%20a%20Tesla%20to%20Alaska%20(REMOTE)%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Model%20X%20has%20an%20advertised%20range%20of%20about%20348%20miles%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tesla.com%2Fmodelx%23%3A~%3Atext%3DWith%2520up%2520to%2520348%2520miles%2Cmore%2520time%2520on%2520the%2520road.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla's%20website%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20any%20number%20of%20factor%20can%20cause%20the%20range%20to%20drop%2C%20including%20extreme%20temperatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20YouTuber%20said%20in%20the%20month%20that%20he%20prepared%20for%20the%20road%20trip%20he'd%20learned%20the%20range%20on%20his%20Tesla%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20cut%20it%20due%20to%20the%20cold%20environment%20and%20steep%20roads.%20Instead%20of%20trying%20to%20make%20a%20go%20of%20the%20stretch%20of%20highway%20in%20one%20day%2C%20van%20Kuijck%20said%20he%20stopped%20midway%20to%20trickle-charge%20his%20Model%20X%20at%20an%20RV%20site%20overnight%20on%20his%20way%20into%20Alaska.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wasn't%20panicked%2C%26quot%3B%20van%20Kuijck%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20willing%20to%20wait%20however%20long%20it%20took%20to%20charge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20YouTuber%20said%20he%20ended%20up%20needing%20only%20an%20additional%2010%25%20of%20battery%20life%20to%20thread%20the%20needle%20and%20make%20it%20through%20the%20dead%20zone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20when%20he%20made%20his%20way%20back%20along%20the%20same%20stretch%20of%20highway%20on%20his%20way%20home%2C%20the%20YouTuber%20said%20he%20drove%20near%20the%20minimum%20speed%20on%20the%20highway%20%E2%80%94%20clocking%2042%20miles%20per%20hour%20in%20a%2065%20miles%20p