ing%20Billionaires%2C%20Hollywood%20Stars%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnited%20Kingdom's%20Prince%20William%20has%20been%20named%20the%20%26quot%3Bsexiest%20bald%20man%20of%202023%26quot%3B%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20study%20based%20on%20Google%20searches.%20Marketing%20agency%20Reboot%20conducted%20the%20study%20by%20analysing%20how%20many%20times%20the%20Prince%20of%20Wales%20had%20been%20searched%20for%2C%20alongside%20the%20words%20%26quot%3Bshirtless%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bnaked%26quot%3B.They%20also%20looked%20at%20celebrities'%20heights%2C%20net%20worths%20and%20how%20shiny%20their%20scalps%20are%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20total%20%26quot%3Bsexy%26quot%3B%20score%20out%20of%2010.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20a%20list%20was%20made%20in%20which%20Prince%20William%20topped%20with%20a%20total%20score%20of%209.88.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20study%2C%20Prince%20William's%20net%20worth%20is%20close%20to%20100%20million%20dollars.%20His%20height%20is%201.91%20metres.%20The%20royal%20received%2037%2C200%20%26quot%3Bshirtless%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bnaked%26quot%3B%20searches%20yearly.%20In%20%26quot%3Bvocal%20attractiveness%2C%26quot%3B%20Prince%20William%20got%20a%20score%20of%209.91%20out%20of%2010%20and%20in%20%26quot%3Bshine%26quot%3B%20factor%20he%20got%208.90%20out%20of%2010.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20royal%20dethroned%20Vin%20Diesel%2C%20last%20year's%20winner%2C%20who%20is%20now%20in%20second%20place%20after%20Hollywood%20star%20Jason%20Statham.%20Samuel%20L%20Jackson%20came%20fourth%20and%20billionaire%20and%20Amazon%20founder%20Jeff%20Bezos%20came%20fifth%2C%20with%20a%20total%20score%20of%207.12%20out%20of%2010.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indy100.com%2Fcelebrities%2Fprince-william-sexiest-bald-man%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3DTwitter%23Echobox%3D1700148257%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndy100%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mr%20Bezos'%20net%20worth%20of%20145%2C000%20million%20dollars%20