m%20to%20resign%20from%20the%20Finding%20Committee%2C%20make%20us%20very%20doubtful%20if%20this%20prerequisite%20for%20any%20coming%20edition%20of%20Documenta%20is%20currently%20given%20in%20Germany.%20Art%20requires%20a%20critical%20and%20multi-perspective%20examination%20of%20its%20diverse%20forms%20and%20contents%20to%20be%20able%20to%20resonate%20and%20develop%20its%20transformative%20capacity.%20Categorical%2C%20one-sided%20reductions%20and%20over-simplifications%20of%20complex%20contexts%20threaten%20to%20nip%20any%20such%20examination%20in%20the%20bud%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20wrote%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHoskote%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fcurator-ranjit-hoskote-resigns-from-documentas-finding-committee-over-anti-semitism-allegations%5C%22%3Eresignation%3C%2Fa%3E%20followed%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sueddeutsche.de%2Fkultur%2Franjit-hoskote-documenta-antisemitismus-bds-1.6301063%3Freduced%3Dtrue%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20daily%20%3Cem%3ES%C3%BCddeutsche%20Zeitung%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20November%209%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaying%20that%20a%202019%20letter%20signed%20by%20Hoskote%2C%20among%20others%2C%20was%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fdocumenta-committee-resigns-in-wake-of-antisemitism-claims%2Fa-67406086%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclearly%20antisemitic%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20culture%20minister%20Claudia%20Roth%20threatened%20to%20withdraw%20public%20funding%20for%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202019%20letter%20was%20published%20as%20part%20of%20the%20article%20in%20%3Cem%3ESuddeutsche%20Zeitung%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0on%20November%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%2C%20circulated%20by%20the%20Boycott%2C%20Divestment%2C%20and%20Sanctions%20(BDS)%20global%20movement%2C%20aimed%20to%20exert%20pressure%20on%20Tel%20Aviv%20to%20withdraw%20from%20the%20occupied%20Palestinian%20territories%20and%20adhere%20to%20human%20rights%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEttinger%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20on%20November%2012%20was%20unrelated%20to%20the%20controversy%20surrounding%20Hoskote.%20%3Cem%3EARTnews%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20her%20decision%20was%20prompted%20by%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdark%20times%E2%80%9D%20affecting%20her%20country%2C%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20letter%2C%20the%20four%20members%20said%20that%20they%20understand%20that%20in%20view%20of%20its%20past%2C%20Germany%20has%20%E2%80%9Cdistinct%20social%20and%20political%20responsibilities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20great%20sensitivity%20towards%20all%20anti-Semitic%20tendencies%20bears%20eloquent%20witness%20to%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20the%20nation%20has%20internalised%20this%20responsibility.%20The%20ongoing%20fulfilment%20of%20this%20very%20responsibility%20deserves%20the%20greatest%20appreciation%2C%20especially%20now%2C%20when%20alarming%20signs%20of%20deep-rooted%20anti-Semitism%20are%20once%20again%20making%20themselves%20felt%20around%20the%20world.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20however%2C%20this%20awareness%20of%20special%20responsibilities%20runs%20the%20risk%20of%20being%20misused%20for%20opinion%20politics%20in%20order%20to%20suppress%20undesirable%20approaches%20and%20their%20broad%20and%20open%20discussion%20right%20from%20the%20start.%20Instead%20of%20debate%20and%20discussion%2C%20over-simplification%20and%20prejudgments%20are%20thus%20all%20too%20easily%20substituted%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20edition%20as%20well%2C%20the%20exhibition%20was%20engulfed%20in%20a%20scandal%20around%20its%20alleged%20proximity%20to%20BDS%20and%20a%20dispute%20over%20anti-Semitic%20iconography.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20members%20said%20in%20the%20letter%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20this%20emotional%20and%20intellectual%20climate%20of%20over-simplification%20of%20complex%20realities%20and%20its%20resulting%20restrictive%20limitations%2C%20which%20has%20been%20prevalent%20since%20documenta15%20and%20especially%20against%20the%20background%20of%20the%20current%20crises%20our%20world%20is%20facing%2C%20that%20makes%20it%20impossible%20for%20us%20to%20conceive%20of%20a%20strong%20and%20signal%20exhibition%20project%2C%20and%20consequently%20to%20allow%20for%20a%20responsible%20continuation%20of%20the%20selection%20process%20to%20determine%20a%20curatorial%20concept%20for%20documenta16.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Finding%20Committee%2C%20according%20to%20the%20organisers%2C%20%E2%80%9Chas%20the%20task%20of%20inviting%20pioneering%20figures%20in%20contemporary%20art%20to%20apply%20to%20take%20on%20the%20role%20of%20Artistic%20Direction%20of%20documenta%2016%2C%20and%20to%20select%20the%20most%20promising%20format%20from%20the%20concepts%20presented.%20Appointment%20of%20the%20Artistic%20Direction%20is%20targeted%20for%20late%202023%20%2F%20early%202024.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20four%20members%20said%20that%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20current%20developments%2C%20there%20is%20no%20space%20for%20%E2%80%9Copen%20exchange%20of%20ideas%E2%80%9D%20in%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20current%20circumstances%20we%20do%20not%20believe%20that%20there%20is%20a%20space%20in%20Germany%20for%20an%20open%20exchange%20of%20ideas%20and%20the%20development%20of%20complex%20and%20nuanced%20artistic%20approaches%20that%20documenta%20artists%20and%20curators%20deserve.%20We%20do%20not%20believe%20that%20any%20acceptable%20conditions%20can%20be%20created%20in%20short%20term%20and%20consider%20it%20to%20be%20disrespectful%20of%20documenta%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20to%20simply%20remain%20content%20with%20the%20current%20situation%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20four%20members%E2%80%99%20letter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20Hoskote%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20on%20November%2012%2C%20Ettinger%20had%20also%20stepped%20down%C2%A0%20for%20reasons%20that%20she%20stated%20were%20not%20connected%20to%20the%20accusations%20levelled%20against%20Hoskote%20but%20because%20Israel%20was%20enduring%20%E2%80%9Cdark%20times.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700301880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F18153253%2Fimage-1520.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fno-space-in-germany-for-open-exchange-of-ideas-after-hoskote-other-documenta-panel-members-quit%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mumbai-based%20author%20and%20curator%20Ranjit%20Hoskote%20resigned%20from%20the%20Finding%20Committee%C2%A0for%20the%20upcoming%2016th%20edition%20of%20Documenta%20in%20Kassel%2C%20Germany%20last%20week%20amid%20accusations%20of%20'anti-Semitism'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fno-space-in-germany-for-open-exchange-of-ideas-after-hoskote-other-documenta-panel-members-quit%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chick-fil-A%20sells%20wings%20through%20a%20spinoff%20restaurant%20called%20Little%20Blue%20Menu.%20I%20tried%20them%20and%20liked%20them%20a%20lot%20better%20than%20CFA's%20signature%20chicken%20sandwich.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side-by-side%20images%20of%20Insider%20reporter%20Alex%20Bitter%20standing%20outside%20the%20Little%20Blue%20Menu%20in%20College%20Park%2C%20Maryland%2C%20and%20a%20close-up%20of%20chicken%20wings%20at%20Little%20Blue%20Menu.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6554edb536d588dc55d0d49b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELittle%20Blue%20Menu%20is%20Chick-fil-A's%20attempt%20to%20break%20into%20two%20new%20menu%20items%3A%20chicken%20wings%20and%20burgers.%20%3Cp%3EAlex%20Bitter%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChick-fil-A%20opened%20the%20first%20physical%20location%20of%20Little%20Blue%20Menu%2C%20a%20new%20restaurant%2C%20in%20Maryland.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELittle%20Blue%20Menu%20serves%20many%20Chick-fil-A%20items%2C%20as%20well%20as%20chicken%20wings%20and%20burgers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20visited%20the%20restaurant%20to%20see%20if%20the%20chicken%20wings%20were%20any%20good.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchick-fil-a-has-slowest-friendliest-drive-thrus-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChick-fil-A%20attracts%20crowds%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20its%20fried%20chicken%20sandwiches.%20But%20the%20company%20is%20trying%20to%20prove%20that%20it%20can%20do%20other%20things%20well%20through%20a%20new%20restaurant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20opened%20its%20first%20permanent%20location%20of%20Little%20Blue%20Menu%20in%20College%20Park%2C%20Maryland%2C%20this%20September.%20The%20restaurant%20sits%20just%20down%20the%20street%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Maryland%20%E2%80%94%20and%20thousands%20of%20hungry%20college%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELittle%20Blue%20Menu%20serves%20up%20two%20things%20you%20won't%20find%20at%20standard%20Chick-fil-A%20restaurants%3A%20Chicken%20wings%20and%20burgers.%20You%20can%20also%20order%20regular%20Chick-fil-A%20menu%20items%2C%20including%20a%20fried%20chicken%20sandwich.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20restaurant%20chain%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20get%20into%20chicken%20wings%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchick-fil-a-opening-a-delivery-restaurant-in-nashville-atlanta-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELittle%20Blue%20Menu%20started%20serving%20food%20in%20Nashville%20and%20Atlanta%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20ghost%20kitchens%2C%20which%20prepare%20food%20for%20delivery%20or%20pick-up%20but%20don't%20have%20dining%20rooms.%20Both%20of%20those%20operations%20appear%20to%20have%20ended.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchick-fil-a-launching-chicken-wing-delivery-concept-restaurant-outfox-trademark-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChick-fil-A%20also%20trademarked%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BOutfox%20Wings%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20find%20out%20if%20Chick-fil-A's%20wings%20are%20any%20good%2C%20I%20went%20to%20Little%20Blue%20Menu%20in%20College%20Park.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20arrived%20at%20Little%20Blue%20Menu%20just%20after%20noon%20on%20a%20Tuesday.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Insider%20reporter%20Alex%20Bitter%20stands%20outside%20of%20a%20Little%20Blue%20Menu%20location%20in%20College%20Park%2C%20Maryland%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654cf7b836d588dc55cdba66%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELittle%20Blue%20Menu's%20College%20Park%20restaurant%20is%20situated%20near%20the%20University%20of%20Maryland%20campus.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Bitter%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20steady%20stream%20of%20diners%20stopping%20by%20for%20lunch%20as%20well%20as%20gig%20workers%20for%20apps%20like%20Uber%20Eats%20and%20DoorDash%20picking%20up%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERight%20away%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20Little%20Blue%20Menu%20is%20leaning%20into%20delivery%20and%20pick-up%20orders.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20sign%20at%20Little%20Blue%20Menu%20directs%20diners%20and%20delivery%20drivers%20to%20separate%20windows%20depending%20on%20whether%20they%20want%20to%20place%20an%20order%2C%20pick%20one%20up%20that%20they%20placed%20via%20a%20mobile%20app%2C%20or%20pick%20up%20an%20order%20as%20a%20delivery%20driver%20for%20a%20third-party%20service%20like%20DoorDash.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654beca736d588dc55cd51ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20sign%20in%20front%20of%20Little%20Blue%20Menu%20directs%20visitors%20to%20one%20of%20three%20areas%20depending%20on%20whether%20they're%20ordering%2C%20picking%20up%20an%20online%20order%2C%20or%20delivering%20food%20through%20a%20third-party%20app.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Bitter%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20isn't%20a%20traditional%20indoor%20dining%20room%20like%20there%20is%20at%20most%20Chick-fil-A%20restaurants.%20Visitors%20are%20guided%20to%20different%20points%20at%20Little%20Blue%20Menu%20depending%20on%20the%20purpose%20of%20their%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere%20was%20a%20dedicated%20pick-up%20point%20for%20gig%20workers%20grabbing%20orders%20for%20third-party%20delivery%20apps.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20door%20at%20Little%20Blue%20Menu%2C%20outside%20of%20which%20delivery%20divers%20for%20Grubhub%2C%20Uber%20Eats%2C%20and%20DoorDash%20can%20wait%20for%20orders.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654beb883cc84b4dfafee3ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGig%20workers%20for%20apps%20like%20DoorDash%20have%20to%20ring%20a%20bell%20to%20pick%20up%20orders.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Bitter%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIndependent%20contractors%20for%20Uber%20Eats%2C%20DoorDash%2C%20and%20GrubHub%20have%20to%20pick%20up%20orders%20by%20ringing%20a%20bell%20outside%20this%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere%20was%20also%20a%20separate%20pick-up%20point%20for%20customers%20who%20had%20ordered%20from%20Little%20Blue%20Menu%20via%20app%20or%20online.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20separate%20door%20for%20pick-up%20orders%20placed%20through%20Chick-fil-A's%20mobile%20app%20at%20the%20Little%20Blue%20Menu%20location%20in%20College%20Park%2C%20Maryland.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654bed8a36d588dc55cd5338%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20pick-up%20point%20for%20online%20and%20app%20orders%20was%20the%20only%20indoor%20area%20that%20customers%20are%20allowed%20in%20at%20Little%20Blue%20Menu.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Bitter%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20must%20have%20looked%20confused%20as%20I%20walked%20around%20to%20the%20different%20pick-up%20points%2C%20since%20an%20employee%20came%20out%20of%20this%20one%20and%20directed%20me%20toward%20the%20line%20to%20place%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EEventually%2C%20I%20made%20my%20way%20to%20this%20line%2C%20where%20walk-up%20customers%20could%20place%20orders.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20sign%20says%20%26quot%3BWalk-up%20orders%26quot%3B%20and%20points%20customers%20toward%20a%20line%20where%20a%20Little%20Blue%20Menu%20employee%20stands%20with%20a%20tablet%20taking%20a%20customer's%20order%20as%20he%20looks%20at%20a%20poster%20with%20the%20restaurant's%20menu.%20In%20the%20background%2C%20signage%20on%20a%20door%20reads%3A%20%26quot%3BLittle%20Blue%20Menu%20team%20members%20only.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654cff55b788914e5553402d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20you%20don't%20order%20online%20or%20through%20a%20delivery%20service%2C%20you%20can%20still%20get%20food%20at%20Little%20Blue%20Menu%20through%20this%20outdoor%20line.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Bitter%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20weren't%20any%20traditional%20cash%20registers%2C%20just%20an%20employee%20with%20a%20tablet%20and%20a%20poster%20with%20the%20menu%20printed%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20menu%20included%20the%20standard%20Chick-fil-A%20offerings%2C%20including%20the%20chain's%20chicken%20sandwich.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Part%20of%20the%20menu%20at%20Little%20Blue%20Menu%2C%20featuring%20items%20you'd%20find%20at%20a%20normal%20Chick-fil-A%20restaurant.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654d0beab788914e5553538b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20menu%20at%20Little%20Blue%20Menu%20was%20extensive%2C%20with%20both%20Chick-fil-A%20staples%20and%20new%20items.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Bitter%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20find%20the%20chicken%20sandwich%2C%20nuggets%2C%20and%20other%20items%20from%20Chick-fil-A%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELower%20down%2C%20I%20found%20what%20I%20was%20looking%20for%3A%20Little%20Blue%20Menu's%20selection%20of%20chicken%20wings.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20menu%20at%20Little%20Blue%20Menu%20includes%20chicken%20wings%20in%20flavors%20such%20as%20traditional%2C%20roasted%20with%20herbs%20and%20garlic%2C%20as%20well%20as%20smoked.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654d0d013cc84b4dfaff74ce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChicken%20wings%20and%20burgers%20are%20both%20prompted%20prominently%20at%20Little%20Blue%20Menu.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Bitter%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20order%20wings%20in%20flavors%20such%20as%20traditional%2C%20roasted%20with%20herbs%20and%20garlic%2C%20as%20well%20as%20smoked.%20You%20can%20also%20opt%20for%20boneless%20wings%20in%20a%20traditional%20coating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhile%20I%20waited%20for%20my%20order%2C%20I%20noticed%20this%20Little%20Blue%20Menu-branded%20delivery%20car.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Little%20Blue%20Menu%20Toyota%20Prius%20delivery%20car%20sits%20in%20a%20parking%20spot%20outside%20the%20restaurant.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654bee0e36d588dc55cd53af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20were%20three%20company-branded%20delivery%20vehicles%20in%20the%20parking%20lot%20when%20I%20visited%20Little%20Blue%20Menu.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Bitter%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20publication%20time%2C%20Little%20Blue%20Menu%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.workstream.us%2Fj%2F30687b62%2Flittle-blue-menu%2Fcollege-park-55917%2Fdelivery-driver-046ee85e%3Flocale%3Den%26referer_source%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.google.com%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewas%20hiring%20drivers%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20deliver%20orders%20in%20the%20restaurant's%20own%20cars%20%26quot%3Bor%20potentially%20by%20e-bike%20in%20a%20safe%20and%20professional%20manner.%26quot%3B%20The%20job%20pays%20%2414%20an%20hour%20plus%20tips%2C%20according%20to%20a%20job%20posting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt%20took%20about%2010%20minutes%20for%20an%20employee%20to%20bring%20my%20order%20out%20to%20me.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20receipt%20on%20the%20side%20of%20a%20Chick-fil-A%20bag%20includes%20the%20order's%20name%20as%20well%20as%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20were%20wearing%20a%20red%20t-shirt%20when%20they%20ordered.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654be9c736d588dc55cd4e36%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAll%20the%20food%20at%20Little%20Blue%20Menu%20is%20packaged%20to-go.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Bitter%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Little%20Blue%20Menu%20is%20a%20new%20restaurant%20concept%2C%20there%20were%20elements%20of%20Chick-fil-A%20branding%20throughout%20my%20experience%20that%20reminded%20me%20which%20brand%20was%20in%20charge.%20The%20employees%20even%20responded%20to%20my%20%26quot%3BThank%20you%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20signature%20Chick-fil-A%20%26quot%3BMy%20pleasure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20the%20employee%20who%20took%20my%20order%20had%20to%20note%20on%20their%20tablet%20what%20I%20was%20wearing.%20As%20this%20packaging%20suggests%2C%20it's%20to%20help%20find%20customers%20outside%20when%20an%20order%20is%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThough%20there%20wasn't%20indoor%20seating%2C%20there%20were%20about%20a%20dozen%20outdoor%20tables%20with%20chairs.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Blue%20metal%20tables%20and%20chairs%20with%20umbrellas%20above%20them%20sit%20outside%20a%20Little%20Blue%20Menu%20location%20in%20College%20Park%2C%20Maryland.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654bea8036d588dc55cd4eee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAll%20the%20outdoor%20furniture%20was%2C%20not%20surprisingly%2C%20blue.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Bitter%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20balmy%2070%20degrees%20when%20I%20visited%2C%20but%20this%20outdoor%20seating%20would%20be%20far%20less%20pleasant%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20winter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20made%20my%20way%20to%20one%20of%20the%20tables%20and%20started%20unpacking%20my%20meal.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chick-fil-A%20drinks%20in%20disposable%20cups%20and%20a%20holder%20sit%20on%20a%20blue%20table%20next%20to%20a%20brown%20paper%20bag%20containing%20food%20from%20the%20fast%20food%20restaurant.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654beabeb788914e5552c53d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20order%20came%20in%20a%20mix%20of%20Chick-fil-A%20and%20Little%20Blue%20Menu%20packaging.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Bitter%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ordered%20several%20items%20on%20this%20visit%2C%20including%20a%20chicken%20sandwich%20and%20some%20wings%20with%20traditional%20seasoning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3