C%20I%20had%20said%20that%20if%20at%20all%20anyone%20can%20come%20closer%20to%20Sachin's%20100s%2C%20it%20will%20be%20Kohli.%20I%20didn't%20expect%20that%20he%20is%20going%20to%20break%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Viswanath%20told%20PTI%20during%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20consistency%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20all%20are%20talking%20about%20his%20hundreds%20but%20the%20way%20he%20has%20been%20getting%2070s%20and%2080s%2C%20any%20batsman%20will%20take%20that.%20It%20is%20(only)%20because%20of%20his%20consistency%20that%20he%20got%2050-plus%20scores.%20The%20way%20he%20approaches%20his%20cricket%2C%20he%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20cricket%20in%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20not%20many%20who%20can%20come%20closer%2C%20even%20though%20Rohit%20(Sharma)%20has%20around%2030%20plus%20hundreds%2C%20so%20(there%20is)%20still%20a%20long%20way%20(to%20go)%20for%20him%2C%20but%20rest%20I%20can't%20pinpoint%20somebody%20is%20there%20to%20come%20close.%20He%20has%20achieved%20one%20hell%20of%20a%20thing%20scoring%20one%20more%20than%20Sachin%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2050%20ODI%20centuries%2C%20Kohli%20also%20has%2029%20hundreds%20in%20Tests%20and%20one%20in%20T20Is%20for%20a%20total%20of%2080%20scores%20above%20100.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20semifinal%2C%20Kohli%20also%20became%20the%20first%20batter%20ever%20to%20break%20the%20700-run%20barrier%20in%20a%20single%20World%20Cup%20edition%20with%20one%20more%20game%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20comparing%20him%20with%20Sachin%20because%20they%20are%20two%20different%20cricketers%2C%20(there%20are)%20no%20comparisons%20but%20both%20are%20great%2C%20absolutely%20legends.%20The%20best%20part%20is%20they%20know%20what%20they%20are%20doing.%20Sachin%20knew%20what%20he%20was%20doing%20and%20Kohli%20said%20he%20is%20my%20guru%20and%20he%20is%20going%20along%20the%20way%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20amazing%2C%20Kohli's%2