m%20I%20could%20share%20my%20happiness%2C%20but%20this%20time%20we%20have%20so%20many%20Astrotalk%20users%20who%20are%20more%20like%20friends%2C%20so%20I%20must%20do%20something%20to%20share%20my%20happiness%20with%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20expressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EDriven%20by%20this%20sentiment%2C%20Mr%20Gupta%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20this%20morning%20I%20spoke%20to%20my%20finance%20team%20and%20pledged%20to%20distribute%C2%A0%E2%82%B9%C2%A0100%20crore%20to%20our%20users%20in%20their%20wallets%20if%20India%20wins%20the%20World%20Cup.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BLet's%20just%20pray%2C%20support%2C%20and%20cheer%20for%20India.%20Indiaaaaa%20India!!!%20Hugs%20in%20advance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fembed%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Ashare%3A7131270068377681920%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Embedded%20post%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22895%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIndia%2C%20led%20by%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20will%20face%20five-time%20world%20champion%20Australia%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%202023%20final%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700299920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Ful0qnp0o_narendra-modi-stadium-afp_625x300_17_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fworld-cup-2023-astrotalk-ceo-puneet-gupta-to-give-away-100-crore-if-india-wins-4584864%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%2C%20led%20by%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20will%20face%20five-time%20world%20champion%20Australia%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%202023%20final%20on%20Sunday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fworld-cup-2023-astrotalk-ceo-puneet-gupta-to-give-away-100-crore-if-india-wins-4584864%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22http