wreck%20hunters%20after%20a%20Bloomberg%20Businessweek%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Ffeatures%2F2023-deep-sea-treasure-hunter-hedge-funds%2F%3Fsrnd%3Dpremium%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvestigation%3C%2Fa%3E%20uncovered%20his%20decades-long%20hunt%20for%20sunken%20treasure%20worth%20billions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthony%20Clake%2C%20a%2043-year-old%20executive%20at%20Marshall%20Wace%20in%20London%2C%20has%20not%20been%20going%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20ocean%20himself%2C%20however.%20He's%20been%20investing%20in%20and%20directing%20high-tech%20operations%20to%20find%20lost%20treasures%20on%20the%20ocean%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarshall%20Wace%20is%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20biggest%20hedge%20funds%2C%20managing%20assets%20worth%20about%20%2462%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Bloomberg%2C%20Clake%20has%20quietly%20spearheaded%20treasure%20hunts%20using%20advanced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstanfords-humanoid-robot-found-treasure-in-ocean-2016-4%23oceanone-was-created-by-a-stanford-team-led-by-oussama-khatib-a-professor-of-computer-science-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderwater%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%20including%20million-dollar%20marine%20robots%20that%20can%20descend%20to%20depths%20of%206%2C000%20meters%2C%20and%20a%20sonar%20system%20that%20creates%203D%20maps%20of%20the%20seabed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%20has%20allowed%20wealthy%20individuals%20like%20Clake%20to%20fund%20exploration%20of%20the%20seabeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClake's%20successes%20include%20the%20SS%20Coloradan%2C%20an%20American%20steamer%20sunk%20by%20a%20German%20U-boat%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20South%20Africa.%20Found%20by%20his%20contractors%20in%202016%2C%20the%20wreck%20contained%20drums%20of%20gold%20precipitate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20ship%20found%20at%20at%20depth%20of%204%2C500%20meters%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20west%20Africa%20contained%2050%20tons%20of%20silver%20coins.%20The%20discovery%20was%20kept%20secret%2C%20the%20coins%20melted%20down%20and%20sold%2C%20and%20everyone%20involved%20had%20to%20sign%20an%20NDA%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20isn't%20clear%20how%20much%20money%20Clake%20has%20made%20from%20the%20salvaged%20treasure.%20But%20often%20the%20most%20lucrative%20wrecks%20draw%20competing%20claims%2C%20legal%20battles%2C%20and%20seizures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20the%20San%20Jos%C3%A9%2C%20a%20Spanish%20galleon%20sunk%20off%20the%20Colombian%20coast%2C%20was%20discovered%20by%20a%20Clake-affiliated%20company.%20It%20contained%20bounty%20thought%20to%20be%20worth%20billions%20of%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20competing%20claims%20from%20another%20US%20treasure-hunting%20entity%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Colombian%20government%20and%20a%20Bolivian%20indigenous%20group%2C%20have%20halted%20plans%20to%20recover%20items%20from%20the%20San%20Jos%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20times%2C%20in%20a%20move%20known%20as%20%26quot%3Bwet%20storage%2C%26quot%3B%20Clake's%20crews%20would%20sometimes%20leave%20their%20finds%20at%20a%20different%20location%20underwater%20to%20avoid%20such%20governmental%20interference%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20how%20much%20Clake%20has%20made%20from%20his%20treasure%20hunting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20do%20it%20for%20a%20living%2C%26quot%3B%20Clake%20told%20Bloomberg%20in%20a%20brief%20interview.%20%26quot%3BI%20find%20it%20interesting%20to%20use%20technology%20to%20solve%20problems%20under%20the%20sea.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETreasure%20hunting%20is%20not%20illegal%2C%20but%20under%20international%20law%20anyone%20who%20discovers%20a%20shipwreck%20must%20report%20their%20findings%20to%20authorities%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lawinfo.com%2Fresources%2Fadmiralty-maritime%2Fare-finders-keepers-under-the-sea-what-you-ne.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELaw%20Info%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%2