n%20Christmas%20(December%2025).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20India%20will%20take%20on%20Australia%20in%20the%20ICC%20ODI%20World%20Cup%202023%20final%20on%20November%2019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhmedabad's%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%20will%20host%20the%20match%2C%20which%20is%20scheduled%20to%20commence%20at%202%3A00%20PM%20IST.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Australia%20are%20targetting%20their%20record-extending%20sixth%20ICC%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20title%2C%20India%2C%20who%20are%20without%20an%20international%20title%20since%20the%202013%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20are%20aiming%20for%20their%20third%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20title%20after%201983%20and%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700297460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-05%2Fbeg4ek38_delhi-liquor-shop-pti_650x400_05_May_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Find-vs-aus-why-delhi-has-declared-a-dry-day-on-nov-19-day-of-world-cup-final-chhath-puja-2023-4584780%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20has%20declared%20a%20'dry%20day'%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20day%20when%20Rohit%20Sharma-led%20Team%20India%20aims%20to%20clinch%20its%20third%20ICC%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20title%20when%20they%20lock%20horns%20with%20Australia%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%202023%20final.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Find-vs-aus-why-delhi-has-declared-a-dry-day-on-nov-19-day-of-world-cup-final-chhath-puja-2023-4584780%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Find-vs-aus-why-delhi-has-declared-a-dry-day-on-nov-19-day-of-world-cup-final-chhath-puja-2023-4584780%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Find-vs-aus-why-delhi-has-declared-a-dry-day-on-nov-19-day-of-world-cup-final-chhath-puja-2023-4584780%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20launches%20major%20drone%20attack%20on%20