ervation%20action%20as%20his%20hobby.%20Whenever%20he%20gets%20a%20chance%2C%20he%20sets%20out%20in%20the%20forest%20to%20collect%20and%20conserve%20wild%20orchids.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGiving%20back%20to%20Mother%20Earth%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20any%20experience%20in%20agricultural%20studies%2C%20Sabu%20started%20his%20own%20initiative.%20He%20follows%20the%20approach%20of%20collection%2C%20conservation%2C%20and%20augmentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirstly%2C%20he%20collects%20wild%20orchids%20that%20grow%20on%20tree%20trunks%2C%20rocks%2C%20and%20rock%20fissures.%20After%20understanding%20the%20environment%20required%20to%20grow%20them%2C%20he%20nurtures%20and%20propagates%20them%20at%20his%20home.%20Thereafter%2C%20he%20replants%20the%20plant%20species%20to%20its%20native%20environment%20%E2%80%94%20near%20the%20mother%20plant%20%E2%80%94%20without%20harming%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20this%2C%20Sabu%20observes%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20plant%20and%20documents%20it%20in%20his%20diary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSabu-1-1700226314.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sabu%20collects%20wild%20orchids%20that%20grow%20on%20tree%20trunks%2C%20rocks%2C%20and%20rock%20fissures.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSabu-1-1700226314.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSabu-1-1700226314-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSabu-1-1700226314-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSabu-1-1700226314-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSabu-1-