%20with%20just%2021%20MLAs%20%E2%80%93%20we%20went%20from%2021%20to%20100%2C%20and%20this%20time%20we%20are%20in%20power%20and%20have%20a%20report%20card%20to%20show%20the%20public%20what%20we%20have%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20373px)%2085vw%2C%20373px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22373%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-1024x845.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22307%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20will%20find%20an%20environment%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20which%20is%20also%20present%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Telangana.%20The%20BJP%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20done%20any%20work%20as%20an%20opposition%20party%20in%20the%20state%20%E2%80%93%20I%20believe%20people%20have%20seen%20their%20ten%20years%20of%20work%20in%20the%20country%20also%2C%20and%20shortcomings%20in%20it%20have%20also%20become%20apparent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20public%20has%20to%20find%20a%20better%20option%2C%20and%20that%20is%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20youth%20like%20you%20very%20much%20but%20have%20been%20angry%20over%20paper%20leaks%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years.%20If%20we%20calculate%20the%20average%2C%20three%20papers%20have%20been%20leaked%20every%20year%20since%202019.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20I%20agree%2C%20paper%20leaks%20are%20a%20big%20issue%20here%20in%20Rajasthan%3B%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20compromise%20with%20this%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20has%20the%20right%20to%20play%20with%20the%20future%20of%20our%20youth.%20We%20can%E2%80%99t%20compromise%20on%20this%20issue.%20Paper%20leaks%20are%20a%20problem%20in%20other%20states%20too.%20I%E2%80%99m%20happy%20that%20my%20party%20has%20listened%20to%20my%20concern%2C%20and%20the%20punishment%20for%20paper%20leaks%20in%20our%20state%20is%20life%20imprisonment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20government%20cares%20for%20the%20students%3A%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20it%20is%20the%20first%20government%20in%20the%20state%20who%20has%20made%20a%20law%20on%20paper%20leaks%2C%20and%20hence%20the%20harshest%20punishment%20has%20been%20provided%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22At%20Tijara%2C%20Rajasthan's%20'Yogi'%20Talks%20of%20Rising%20Above%20Caste%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmahant-baba-balaknath-rajasthan-election-yogi-adityanath%5C%22%3EAt%20Tijara%2C%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Yogi%E2%80%99%20Talks%20of%20Rising%20Above%20Caste%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20spoke%20about%20the%20youth%20%E2%80%93%20there%20is%20one%20more%20issue%20that%20we%20have%20been%20seeing%20in%20Rajasthan.%20In%20Kota%2C%20we%20see%20thousands%20of%20students%20coming%20every%20year%20to%20prepare%20for%20%5Bthe%20JEE%20and%20NEET%5D.%20This%20year%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20over%2025%20suicides.%20What%20is%20the%20solution%3F%20Because%20students%20from%20the%20entire%20country%20come%20to%20Kota.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20very%20unfortunate%20that%20suicide%20incidents%20are%20increasing%20in%20Kota.%20This%20is%20also%20a%20social%20problem.%20Lakhs%20of%20children%20come%20to%20study%3B%20we%20are%20also%20providing%20counselling%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20what%20is%20the%20solution%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20to%20think%20about%20it%3B%20failure%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20looked%20down%20upon.%20These%20are%20societal%20issues%2C%20young%20people%20committing%20suicide%20%E2%80%93%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20worst%20thing%20for%20any%20country%20or%20any%20society.%20I%20am%20very%20sad%20about%20these%20things%20coming%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20supremo%20Mayawati%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fbsp-will-contest-from-all-200-seats-in-rajasthan-says-party-leader%2Farticleshow%2F103182478.cms%5C%22%3Esaid%20her%20party%20will%20be%20contesting%20all%20200%20seats%20in%20Rajasthan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20BSP%20has%20influence%20over%20Scheduled%20Caste%20(SC)%20votes.%20Do%20you%20think%20it%20can%20affect%20the%20Congress%3F%20As%20we%20have%20seen%20in%20the%202018%20election%2C%20the%20Congress%20%5Bwhich%20went%20on%20to%20form%20the%20government%5D%20won%20more%20SC%20seats%20than%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20parties%20contest%20elections%2C%20but%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20elections%20are%20held%20mainly%20between%20only%20two%20parties%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP.%20These%20parties%20have%20been%20contesting%20before%20also%3B%20parties%20apart%20from%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20might%20get%20one%20or%20two%20seats%2C%20but%20the%20main%20contest%20will%20always%20be%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELook%20at%20these%20regional%20parties%2C%20what%20is%20their%20situation%20in%20their%20own%20state%3F%20So%20I%20believe%20that%20people%20from%20all%20sections%20of%20society%20stand%20with%20the%20Congress%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frajasthan-congress-bjp-battle-bsp-influence-electoral-outcome%5C%22%3EAs%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20Battle%20for%20Rajasthan%2C%20Can%20BSP%20Influence%20Electoral%20Outcome%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20about%20Hanuman%20Beniwal%E2%80%99s%20Rashtriya%20Loktantrik%20Party%2C%20which%20is%20also%20contesting%20this%20%3Cem%3Evidhan%20sabha%3C%2Fem%3E%20election%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESee%2C%20I%20told%20you%20%E2%80%93%20many%20parties%20contest%20elections%20here%2C%20but%20the%20competition%20is%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20only.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20same%20for%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20also.%20These%20parties%20may%20get%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20the%20vote%20share%2C%20but%20I%20am%20telling%20you%2C%20for%20every%20society%2C%20whether%20urban%20or%20rural%2C%20the%20Congress%20party%20is%20a%20better%20place%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%202013%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fassembly-elections-2013%2Frajasthan%2Fstory%2Frajasthan-election-bjp-win-biggest-ever-congress-loss-biggest-ever-220101-2013-12-07%5C%22%3ECongress%20experienced%20its%20worst%20defeat%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20the%20party%20had%20only%2021%20MLAs%20left%20%E2%80%93%20after%20which%20the%20elections%20of%202018%20were%20imposed%20under%20your%20leadership.%20But%20why%20did%20the%20party%20still%20not%20make%20you%20the%20chief%20minister%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20this%20is%20right%3B%20we%20were%2021%20only%2C%20and%20we%20struggled%20a%20lot%20to%20make%20it%20100%20in%20Rajasthan.%20We%20struggled%20for%20five%20years%2C%20on%20the%20street%20%E2%80%93%20we%20faced%20lathi%20charges%2C%20we%20went%20to%20jail%2C%20we%20staged%20protests%2C%20yatras%20and%20gheraos%20%E2%80%93%20and%20it%20is%20after%20this%20that%20the%20people%20blessed%20us%20and%20put%20us%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20always%20say%20that%20governments%20are%20made%20by%20parties%2C%20but%20the%20reverse%20isn%E2%80%99t%20true.%20Our%20first%20priority%20is%20that%20the%20party%20organisation%20should%20remain%20strong.%20Then%2C%20after%20the%20elections%20and%20after%20the%20opinion%20of%20the%20MLAs%2C%20it%20will%20be%20decided%20who%20should%20be%20given%20what%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20we%20all%20have%20the%20same%20objective%3A%20seeing%20how%20we%20can%20form%20a%20strong%20Congress%20government%20here.%20There%20is%20a%20need%20for%20a%20stronger%20Congress%20when%20we%20form%20governments%20in%20different%20states%20of%20the%20country%3B%20hence%20the%20Rajasthan%20election%20is%20important%20for%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPeople%20are%20going%20to%20vote%20in%20Rajasthan%20in%2010%20days%20%5Bfrom%20the%20date%20of%20the%20interview%5D%3B%20why%20is%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20not%20campaigning%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20is%20here%20only%2C%20and%20he%20will%20be%20here%20till%20November%2023%3B%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20and%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20all%20have%20programmes%20here.%20Today%2C%20i.e.%2C%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20November%2015%2C%20the%20election%20campaign%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20has%20ended.%20You%20will%20meet%20everyone%20here%20till%20November%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Emergence%20as%20Another%20Hindutva%20Laboratory%20Keeps%20BJP%20Afloat%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmadhya-pradesh-hindutva-laboratory-bjp-afloat%5C%22%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Emergence%20as%20Another%20Hindutva%20Laboratory%20Keeps%20BJP%20Afloat%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20your%20opinion%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20safety%2C%20which%20the%20BJP%20is%20continuously%20raising%20in%20Rajasthan%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESee%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20safety%20should%20be%20a%20top%20priority%20and%20should%20not%20be%20politicised.%20It%20is%20mandatory%20to%20register%20an%20FIR%20for%20any%20incident%20that%20happens%20in%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20do%20not%20try%20to%20suppress%20the%20incidents.%20What%20is%20happening%20in%20UP%20or%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%A6%20everyone%20knows%20that%20there%20are%20things%20happening%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20which%20are%20exposed%20later.%20Here%2C%20we%20do%20not%20try%20to%20suppress%20the%20facts%20around%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20priority%20here%20is%20that%20%E2%80%A6%20whatever%20incident%20happens%2C%20how%20quickly%20we%20take%20action%20on%20it%20and%20how%20quickly%20we%20get%20the%20culprit%20punished%20is%20our%20priority.%20We%20have%20done%20strong%20work%20in%20that%20direction%20%E2%80%93%20there%20is%20always%20room%20for%20improvement%2C%20and%20we%20will%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20BJP%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20issues%20to%20raise%2C%20do%20they%3F%20Cylinder%20prices%20are%20at%20an%20all-time%20high%20and%20so%20are%20those%20of%20petrol%20and%20diesel.%20How%20high%20is%20unemployment%3F%20Can%20anyone%20imagine%20by%20how%20much%20the%20gap%20between%20the%20rich%20and%20the%20poor%20has%20increased%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20government%20has%20sold%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20airports%2C%20railways%2C%20ports%2C%20power%20plants%20and%20mines%20at%20throwaway%20prices.%20The%20incomes%20of%20farmers%20have%20not%20even%20doubled%3B%20the%20BJP%20does%20not%20even%20have%20its%20report%20card%20to%20show%2C%20so%20they%20are%20pointing%20fingers%20at%20others.%20People%20will%20reply%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Congress%20party%20is%20giving%20seven%20guarantees%20in%20Rajasthan%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E(1)%20an%20annual%20honorarium%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000%20to%20women%20heads%20of%20family%2C%20(2)%20cooking%20gas%20cylinders%20at%20Rs%20500%20to%201.05%20crore%20families%2C%20(3)%20the%20purchase%20of%20dung%20from%20cattle%20rearers%20at%20Rs%202%20per%20kg%2C%20(4)%20a%20law%20for%20the%20old%20pension%20scheme%20for%20government%20employees%2C%20(5)%20a%20laptop%20or%20tablet%20to%20students%20taking%20admission%20in%20government%20colleges%2C%20(6)%20insurance%20cover%20up%20to%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20per%20family%20to%20compensate%20for%20losses%20due%20to%20natural%20calamities%20and%20(7)%20school%20education%20in%20the%20English%20medium.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20where%20will%20the%20party%20bring%20the%20funds%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F_ZFnLrfJx5M%3Fsi%3DPQNNwqPXUJVwYB2V%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20fiscal%20management%20is%20much%20better%20than%20in%20other%20states.%20We%20launch%20our%20schemes%20with%20great%20responsibility.%20Mainly%2C%20the%20tax-paying%20public%E2%80%99s%20money%20should%20go%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20people%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20pension%3B%20children%20should%20get%20food%20in%20school%3B%20there%20should%20be%20social%20welfare%20programs%20and%20they%20should%20get%20scholarships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20this%20better%2C%20or%20is%20it%20better%20to%20forgive%20industrialists%E2%80%99%20debts%20worth%20crores%20of%20rupees%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20about%20priorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20has%20been%20continuously%20attacking%20Adani%2C%20but%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fbe-it-adani-ambani-or-jay-shah-we-welcome-all-rajasthan-cm-gehlot%2Farticle65984607.ece%5C%22%3EAshok%20Gehlot%20is%20seen%20on%20the%20same%20stage%20with%20Adani%3C%2Fa%3E.%20How%20do%20you%20see%20these%20two%20sides%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESee%2C%20only%20Mr%20Gehlot%20give%20the%20answer%20to%20this%20question%2C%20but%20overall%2C%20we%20want%20to%20end%20capitalism%20in%20the%20country%20and%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20the%20entire%20economy%20to%20be%20run%20by%20a%20few%20people.%20Rahul%20ji%20has%20said%20that%20the%20poor%20should%20have%20the%20first%20right%20over%20state%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(Later%2C%20on%20Adani%2C%20Pilot%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20say%20much%20about%20the%20person%20you%20are%20talking%20about.%E2%80%9D)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIf%20the%20Congress%20comes%20to%20power%2C%20will%20we%20see%20Sachin%20Pilot%20as%20our%20next%20chief%20minister%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20let%20us%20win%20the%20elections%2C%20and%20then%20we%20will%20take%20this%20decision.%20We%20will%20seek%20advice%20from%20legislators%20and%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20top%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20our%20old%20tradition%20for%20decades%20that%20we%20first%20form%20the%20government%20and%20then%20decide%20who%20will%20become%20the%20chief%20minister%20after%20considering%20the%20views%20of%20our%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20members%20and%20our%20party%E2%80%99s%20senior%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20are%20talking%20about%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20MLAs%20or%20even%20the%20decision%20of%20senior%20leaders.%20We%20have%20seen%20in%20September%202022%20how%20MLAs%20have%20different%20opinions%20from%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20senior%20leaders%20about%20the%20post%20of%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParty%20president%20Mr%20Kharge%20told%20me%20to%20forgive%2C%20forget%20and%20move%20forward%2C%20and%20asked%20what%20is%20the%20point%20of%20repeating%20what%20has%20happened%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20to%20look%20ahead%2C%20and%20the%20tradition%20of%20the%20party%20is%20to%20first%20win%20the%20election%20and%20then%20make%20the%20decision%20about%20who%20will%20get%20what.%20Chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20has%20also%20apologised%20for%20the%20incident%20you%20are%20talking%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20text%20of%20this%20interview%20was%20lightly%20edited%20for%20style%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700216543000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17133446%2FPilot.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsachin-pilot-interview-2023-rajasthan-election%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Speaking%20to%20The%20Wire%2C%20the%20former%20Rajasthan%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20also%20spoke%20on%20women's%20safety%20in%20the%20state%20and%20its%20prudent%20fiscal%20management.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsachin-pilot-interview-2023-rajasthan-election%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%E2%80%99s%20PC%20Imports%20Surge%20to%204.5%20million%20After%20Union%20Government%20U-Turn%20on%20Import%20Licenses%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F10125800%2FUntitled-design.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20imports%20of%20personal%20computers%20surged%20to%20a%20record%204.5%20million%20units%20in%20the%20July%20to%20September%20quarter%2C%20recording%20an%20increase%20of%2014%25%20year-over-year%20(YoY)%20according%20to%20data%20from%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.idc.com%2Fgetdoc.jsp%3FcontainerId%3DprAP51395423%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EInternational%20Data%20Corporation%20(IDC)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Worldwide%20Quarterly%20Personal%20Computing%20Device%20Tracker.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20data%20released%20on%20November%2016%2C%20the%20notebook%20category%20grew%20by%2013.1%25%20YoY%2C%20while%20the%20desktop%20category%20grew%20by%2019.3%25.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20traditional%20PC%20market%20includes%20desktops%2C%20notebooks%2C%20and%20workstations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20growth%20comes%20after%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fin-a-u-turn-union-govt-rolls-back-plans-to-license-laptop-computer-imports%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EU-turn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20last%20month%20on%20its%20earlier%20plan%20imposing%20import%20restrictions%20on%20laptops%2C%20tablets%2C%20and%20certain%20types%20of%20computers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20announcement%20on%20October%2019%2C%20came%20months%20after%20the%20government%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgovt-imposes-import-curbs-on-laptops-computers-with-immediate-effect%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eimposed%20import%20restrictions%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eon%20laptops%2C%20tablets%2C%20and%20certain%20types%20of%20computers%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%20citing%20%E2%80%9Csecurity%20reasons%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20need%20to%20promote%20domestic%20manufacturing%20on%20August%203.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20then%20had%20also%20said%20that%20those%20wanting%20to%20import%20these%20items%20would%20need%20a%20license%20starting%20November%201.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20consumer%20segment%20saw%20strong%20traction%20in%203Q23%20after%20a%20challenging%20past%20four%20quarters.%20In%20August%2C%20the%20government%20of%20India%20declared%20a%20mandatory%20requirement%20of%20import%20licenses%20for%20PCs%20from%2030%20October.%20Though%20this%20decision%20was%20later%20put%20on%20hold%2C%20vendors%20shipped%20significant%20channel%20inventory%20to%20avoid%20any%20risks%20of%20supply%20shortages%20or%20price%20hikes%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20ensuring%20sufficient%20supplies%20for%20festival%20season%20sales%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bharath%20Shenoy%2C%20senior%20research%20analyst%2C%20IDC%20India%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20IDC%20data%20the%20consumer%20sector%20saw%20a%20rise%20of%2026.3%25%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20year%20but%20the%20commercial%20sector%20remained%20unchanged.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20terms%20of%20personal%20computer%20companies%2C%20HP%20Inc.%20led%20the%20market%20with%20a%20share%20of%2029.4%25%20as%20it%20topped%20the%20charts%20in%20both%20the%20commercial%20and%20consumer%20segments%20with%20shares%20of%2034.3%25%20and%2025.9%25%20respectively%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20IDC%20the%20firm%E2%80%99s%20inventory%20pushes%20and%20positive%20market%20sentiment%20helped%20it%20clock%20its%20biggest%20ever%20consumer%20quarter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELenovo%20came%20second%20with%20a%20share%20of%2017%25%20as%20its%20shipments%20fell%208.8%25%20year%20on%20year.%20In%20the%20desktop%20category%20it%20fared%20well%20and%20witnessed%20year%20on%20year%20growth%20of%2032.5%25%20in%20the%20third%20quarter%20of%202023.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDell%20Technologies%20came%20third%20with%20a%2014.6%25%20market%20share%20and%20a%20year-on-year%20growth%20of%203.8%25.%20IDC%20said%20that%20Lenovo%20had%20not%20decided%20not%20to%20do%20heavy%20stocking%2C%20which%20led%20to%20some%20market%20share%20loss%20but%20helped%20maintain%20healthy%20channel%20inventory.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EASUS%20took%20the%20fourth%20position%20with%20a%2012.5%25%20share%20and%20achieved%20its%20most%20significant%20consumer%20quarter%20by%20surpassing%20500%2C000%20units%20in%20the%20consumer%20segment.%20According%20to%20IDC%20ASUS%20decided%20to%20do%20heavy%20stocking%20for%20festive%20season%20sales%20as%20it%20wanted%20to%20avoid%20any%20supply%20hurdles%20due%20to%20the%20import%20regulations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAcer%20took%20the%20fifth%20spot%20with%2011.6%25%20market%20share%20despite%20a%2020.9%25%20year-on-year%20growth.%20IDC%20said%20that%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20focus%20on%20online%20channels%20contributed%20to%20its%20most%20substantial%20consumer%20quarter%20on%20record.%20The%20firm%20pushed%20stocks%20on%20online%20channels%20and%20had%20its%20biggest%20consumer%20quarter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20the%20increase%20in%20the%20consumer%20segment%2C%20IDC%20said%20that%20in%20the%20PC%20market%20a%20dearth%20of%20enterprise%20orders%20remains%20a%20concern.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20the%20PC%20market%20has%20seen%20a%20substantial%20channel%20push%20in%20the%20consumer%20segment%20and%20to%20some%20extent%20in%20the%20SME%20segment%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Navkendar%20Singh%2C%20Associate%20Vice%20President%2C%20Devices%20Research%2C%20IDC%20India%2C%20South%20Asia%20%26amp%3B%20ANZ.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20vendors%20are%20now%20focused%20on%20increasing%20their%20local%20assembly%20mix%20as%20government%20and%20education%20projects%20are%20expected%20to%20prefer%20locally%20assembled%20devices.%20While%20this%20might%20give%20a%20further%20boost%20to%20the%20government%20and%20education%20segments%2C%20a%20dearth%20of%20enterprise%20orders%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20concern%20as%20the%20enterprise%20segment%20is%20expected%20to%20decline%20by%20over%2020%25%20YoY%20in%202023.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700215580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F10125800%2FUntitled-design.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Findias-pc-imports-surge-to-4-5-million-after-union-government-u-turn-on-import-licenses%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20the%20International%20Data%20Corporation%2C%20vendors%20shipped%20significant%20channel%20inventory%20to%20avoid%20any%20risks%20of%20supply%20shortages%20or%20price%20hikes%2C%20not%20to%20