Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20reiterate%20the%20need%20for%20nations%20to%20respect%20the%20Vienna%20Convention%20on%20diplomatic%20relations%20so%20that%20our%20diplomats%20can%20discharge%20their%20diplomatic%20obligations%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bagchi%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20paper%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20diplomatic%20relations%20with%20Canada%20had%20soured%20after%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20accused%20India%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20pro-Khalistan%20activist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20in%20September.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20strongly%20rejected%20the%20allegations%20and%20responded%20by%20temporarily%20suspending%20visa%20services%20to%20Canadian%20citizens%20and%20asked%20Ottawa%20to%20downsize%20its%20diplomatic%20presence%20in%20the%20country%20to%20ensure%20parity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBagchi%20was%20also%20asked%20about%20an%20incident%20that%20occurred%20near%20Brampton%20on%20Diwali%20which%20he%20called%20an%20%E2%80%9Cunrest%E2%80%9D%20between%20two%20groups.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20regards%20to%20events%20that%20you%20alluded%20to%20near%20Brampton%20on%20Diwali.%20I%20think%20that%20was%20more%20in%20the%20nature%20of%20unrest%20between%20the%20two%20groups.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20there%20has%20been%20any%20complaint%20that%20our%20consulate%20has%20received%E2%80%A6%20I%20saw%20some%20social%20media%20reports.%20We%20also%20understand%20that%20the%20authorities%20there%20are%20looking%20into%20that%20incident%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Findia-calls-on-canada-to-respect-vienna-convention-on-diplomatic-relations-562949%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20fresh%20call%20to%20Ottawa%20comes%20days%20after%20it%20urged%20Canada%20to%20%3Ca%20href