dened%20with%20a%20loan%20of%20Rs%2012%20lakh.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20did%20not%20want%20to%20give%20up%20on%20our%20dream.%20Without%20giving%20up%20hope%2C%20we%20pooled%20some%20money%20and%20went%20to%20cities%20like%20Hyderabad%20and%20Delhi%20to%20meet%20investors%20from%20the%20Taj%20Hotel%2C%20Radisson%20Blu%2C%20and%20Ashoka%20Hotel.%20They%20were%20impressed%20by%20our%20idea%20and%20invested%20in%20our%20work%2C%20and%20finally%2C%20we%20reopened%20our%20restaurant%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuhas%20says%20he%20does%20not%20come%20from%20any%20culinary%20background.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20says%2C%20he%20did%20not%20even%20know%20the%20difference%20between%20%3Cem%3Eurad%20%3C%2Fem%3E(black%20gram)%20and%20%3Cem%3Echana%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Edal%20%3C%2Fem%3E(chickpea).%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20the%20couple%20learnt%20everything%20from%20scratch%20on%20their%20own%20and%20established%20the%20restaurant%20by%20using%20their%20grandma%E2%80%99s%20recipes%20and%20recreating%20delicacies%20from%20South%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Suhas%2C%20the%20journey%20has%20been%20full%20of%20learning%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20feels%20immensely%20contented.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20retire%20to%20my%20bed%2C%20I%20sleep%20peacefully%20knowing%20the%20value%20of%20the%20work%20I%20do.%20With%20this%2C%20I%20am%20able%20to%20revive%20my%20native%20delicacies%20in%20the%20simplest%20form%20with%20high%20nutritional%20value%20%E2%80%94%20just%20the%20way%20my%20grandma%20offered%20it%20to%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20Jagli%20Tindi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700141878000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fjagli-tindi-1-1700140193.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334273%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Craving%20Mangalore%20buns%2C%20mandakki%20upkari%20and%20kho