-heading%5C%22%3ESpearheading%20change%20through%20sports%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDream%20a%20Dream%20works%20with%20both%20affordable%20private%20schools%20and%20State%20Governments.%20For%20instance%2C%20they%20partnered%20with%20the%20Delhi%20government%20and%20other%20nonprofit%20organisations%20to%20implement%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20in-school%20Social%20and%20Emotional%20Learning%20(SEL)%20curriculum%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Happiness%20Curriculum%20%E2%80%94%20launched%20in%202018%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Government%20to%20enhance%20students%E2%80%99%20mindfulness%20and%20positive%20productivity.%20This%20initiative%20positively%20impacts%20eight%20lakh%20children%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fdream-a-dream-2-1700039261.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20initiative%20has%20impacted%20over%202.2%20million%20children%20across%20the%20country.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fdream-a-dream-2-1700039261.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fdream-a-dream-2-1700039261-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fdream-a-dream-2-1700039261-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fdream-a-dream-2-1700039261-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fdream-a-dream-2-1700039261-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334165%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20initiative%20has%20impacted%20over%202.2%20million%20children%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPavithra%2C%2