ivation%2C%20people%20would%20build%20a%20small%20forest%20in%20between%2C%20to%20help%20cross%20pollination.%20The%20birds%20and%20snakes%20in%20the%20forest%20would%20keep%20rats%20and%20insects%20away%20from%20the%20crops.%20The%20forest%20that%20Srikanth%20has%20created%20will%20prevent%20soil%20erosion.%20It%20has%20also%20become%20a%20hub%20for%20birds%2C%20with%20over%2055%20species%20habiting%20the%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Praveen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20says%20that%20had%20Srikanth%20not%20taken%20the%20efforts%20to%20create%20this%20forest%2C%20it%20would%20have%20become%20a%C2%A0sand%20quarry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20success%20of%20this%20forest%2C%20Srikanth%20has%20created%20a%20Miyawaki%20forest%20in%20a%201-acre%20land%20and%20another%20forest%20in%20Pernambut.%20He%20has%20also%20planted%20fruit%20trees%20in%20villages%20across%20Vellore%2C%20which%20would%20help%20villagers%20get%20an%20income%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20goal%20is%20to%20create%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332769%2Fgeorge-remedios-plants-food-forests-trees-in-mumbai-limited-spaces-rooftop-gardens%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20forests%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20wastelands%20across%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20all%20busy%20earning%20assets%20for%20our%20next%20generation.%20I%20believe%20that%20increasing%20the%20green%20cover%20and%20building%20such%20forests%20is%20the%20biggest%20asset%20we%20can%20leave%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Srikanth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699970361000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FMy-work-view-16-1699969285.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334084%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Braving%20threats%20from%20the%20real%20estate%20mafia%2C%20G%